channel.title: How do i enter another player's private server?
channel.description:
ok I really need help,how do I join a private server which has other people playing?
I have no idea where to enter info, there are too many options, such as the ip ping, new port, all that stuff..
so can you please tell me step by step how to join someones server? I just want to play a server with other people.

item.title: How do i enter another player's private server?
item.dc:creator: @J112 J
item.description:
@J112 wrote:

Most servs have the default port (43594).

Ping server is to see if the server is lagging.
